## Design System

### Color Palette

**Brand Colors:**
- Primary: `emerald-500` (#10b981) - CTAs, badges, accents
- Primary Hover: `emerald-400` (#34d399)
- Discord: `#5865F2` (hover: `#4752C4`)

**Neutral Colors:**
- Background: `black` (#000000)
- Surface: `neutral-900` (#171717)
- Surface Alt: `neutral-950` (#0a0a0a) - alternate section backgrounds
- Border: `neutral-800` (#262626)
- Border Hover: `neutral-700` (#404040)

**Text Hierarchy:**
- Primary text: `text-white` - headings, important content
- Secondary text: `text-neutral-300` - body text, descriptions
- Tertiary text: `text-neutral-400` - labels, metadata
- Muted text: `text-neutral-500` - placeholders, less important info

**Status Colors:**
- Success: `emerald-500/10` bg, `emerald-400` text
- Error: `red-500/10` bg, `red-400` text

